          <title>
            <string language="sl">Vodna hijacinta</string>
            <string language="en">Water hyacinth</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wasserhyazinthe</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Jacinthe de l'eau</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Hyacinth da água</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Giacinto dell'acqua</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Υάκινθος ύδατος</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Jacinto del agua</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Plavajoča vodna rastlina, iz tropske Amerike ima vpadljive modro-vijoličaste cvetove ter izrazite listne peclje. Raste na rekah, ribnikih in podobno tvori neprehodne gmote, v južnem delu ZDA, na Javi, v Avstraliji, Novi Zelandiji in v delih Afrike.</string>
            <string language="en">Floating aquatic plant native to tropical America. It has blue-violet petal leaves and distinctive long, spongy stalks. It grows on rivers, ponds and other waters and can easily overgrown large regions (in south USA, Australia, New Zeland, parts of Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">vodna hijacinta</string>
            <string language="en">water hyacinth</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">hijacinta</string>
            <string language="en">hyacinth</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">roža</string>
            <string language="en">flower</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sich hin- und herbewegender 
Wasserpflanzeeingeborener nach tropisches Amerika. Es hat 
blau-violette Blumenblattblätter und unterscheidende lange, 
schwammige Stiele. Es wächst auf Flüssen, Teiche und anderes 
Wasser und Dose leicht überwucherte große Regionen (in Süd-USA, 
Australien, neues Zeland, Teile von Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Indigène flottant d'usine aquatique vers 
l'Amérique tropicale. Elle a les feuilles bleu-violettes de 
pétale et les longues, spongieuses tiges distinctives. Elle se 
développe sur des fleuves, étangs et d'autres eaux et régions 
envahies de bidon facilement grandes (dans sud Etats-Unis, 
Australie, nouveau Zeland, parties d'Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Nativo flutuando da planta aquática a América 
tropical. Tem as folhas azul-violetas da pétala e stalks 
longos, esponjosos distintivos. Cresce em rios, lagoas e outras 
águas e regiões grandes overgrown da lata fàcilmente (em EUA sul, 
Austrália, Zeland novo, partes de Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Nativo di galleggiante della pianta acquatica in 
America tropicale. Ha i fogli blu-viola del petalo e gambi 
lunghi e spugnosi distintivi. Si sviluppa facilmente sui fiumi, 
stagni ed altre acque e regioni invase della latta grandi (negli 
S.U.A. del sud, Australia, nuovo Zeland facente parte Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Επιπλέουσες υδρόβιες εγκαταστάσεις εγγενείς στην 
τροπική Αμερική. Έχει τα μπλε-ιώδη φύλλα πετάλων και τους 
διακριτικούς μακριούς, σπογγώδεις μίσχους. Αυξάνεται στους 
ποταμούς, τις λίμνες και άλλα ύδατα και μπορεί εύκολα μεγάλες 
περιοχές (στο νότο ΗΠΑ, Αυστραλία, νέο Zeland, μέρη Afrika</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Natural flotante de la planta acuática a 
América tropical. Tiene las hojas azul-violetas del pétalo y 
tallos largos, esponjosos distintivos. Crece en los ríos, 
charcas y otras aguas y regiones grandes overgrown de la lata 
fácilmente (en los E.E.U.U. del sur, Australia, Zeland nuevo, partes 
de Afrika</string>
          </description>
